{"tid":1603824,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大日子物資清單","createTime":"2019-09-29T19:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T10:02:00.000Z","uid":40652,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"bd369526506d1fbf7e4bd8a7c1743d87980b511e","tid":1603824,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:00:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">必需：</span></span><br />\n黑衫/黑褲/黑帽/黑口罩/黑冰就/泳鏡<br />\n非黑衫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2</span>件<br />\n毛巾<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2</span>條<br />\n10000mah以上滿電尿袋+叉電線<br />\n火機（食煙用）最好防風<br />\n水 最少2支<br />\n退熱貼<br />\n氣球1-2個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">白電油/</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沙糖/</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">漂白水</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">是但1樣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">非必需：</span></span><br />\n鋼頭鞋<br />\n5mm鐵珠<br />\n士巴拿<br />\n拿鉗<br />\n鎚仔<br />\n鐵筆<br />\n丫叉<br />\n索帶<br />\n介刀/較剪<br />\n鎖匙<br />\n偈油<br />\n花生油<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如當日需要購買飲品，請買玻璃樽裝，飲完放係路邊垃圾桶外等人回收</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外提提大家盡量唔好飲有氣既飲品</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"502c9408a67ccedfdbe0f1bb3d575afb0fd363b1","tid":1603824,"uid":154486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080e9076df2a7d37ec83dd9c4399db22b084fed5","tid":1603824,"uid":93072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:02:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">黑警償命</span></span>